Package: EDIutils
Title: An API Client for the Environmental Data Initiative Repository
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Colin", "Smith", email = "colin.smith@wisc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2261-9931")
Description: The EDI Data Repository (https://portal.edirepository.org/nis/home.jsp) is for the archive and reuse of ecological data, emphasizing data quality and information rich metadata. EDIutils includes functions to search the repository, retrieve metadata, download files, and more.
